The paper deals with the characterization of degrees of freedom (DoF) regions for various MIMO channels, which is a topic related to information theory (cs.IT). The channels considered include interference channels (cs.NI), cognitive radio channels (cs.SI), and broadcast channels (cs.MM), which are all subcategories of communication and networking (cs.COM). Therefore, these are the most likely subcategories for this paper.
